reviewText: I ordered the dvd box with the 3 first seasons, and I just finished watching the first one. It had about 10 different chapters of the Kardashians lives, so if you consider that you payed around 20 bucks per DVD, it is as if you had payed 2 dollares per chapter (each of the 10 chapters last around 40 minutes).
Great dvd!  It's great to see what celebrities do on a day to day basis.  I would buy more seasons.
Really enjoyed this series and am looking forward to new releases. Please hurry and get season four and more as soon as possible.
awesome dvd great price great entertainment fast postage hours of viewing great value for money, very satisfied with dvd set

Great products. No problems at all. Perfect condition!!! Thank you so much. No scratches at all. My sister loves them. Thanks.

My 12-year old daughter and I had a great time watching the Kardashians together. Though it might be sometimes superficial, there is always the sense of family and a great, warm heart. Besides it has a lot of useful advice for young teenagers.
Shipment took a long time, but we knew that beforehand. We are happy, that we can order from the US reliable and at a reasonable rate of shipment.
My college age daughter loved these for Christmas.  Although I'm not crazy about the show, I did enjoy our time on the couch over her break watching the show together so it was very worth it to me.
Love it of course. My guilty pleasure!
